      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Method",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Mix, knead, and bulk ferment, 1 hour",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Mix {{strong-bread-flour}}, {{yeast-fast-action}}, {{salt-table}}, and {{caster-sugar}}. Add the {{whole-milk}}, {{water}}, and {{unsalted-butter}}. Bring together and knead for 8 minutes until smooth. Cover and leave until doubled, about 1 hour.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Shape and prove, 40 minutes",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Line a rectangular tin (roughly 30×20 cm) with baking paper. Divide the dough into 12 equal pieces. Shape each into a tight ball and arrange in a 3×4 grid in the tin. They should fit snugly. Cover and prove for 40 minutes until visibly risen and touching. Heat the oven to 200°C (180°C fan).",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Bake",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Brush gently with milk. Bake for 16 to 18 minutes until golden on top. The centres should be cooked through, lift the tin and check the base is pale gold, not pale and wet. Cool in the tin for 5 minutes before transferring to a rack. Pull apart to serve.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
